text: Abderrahmane Boushita (born 5 September 1997) is a Moroccan judoka. He represented Morocco at the 2019 African Games and won a silver medal in the men's –66 kg category.ABDERRAHMANE BOUSHITA JUDOKA. JudoInside.BOUSHITA ABDERRAHMANE. IJF.org He also competed in Men's 66 kg event at the 2017 World Judo Championships, at the 2018 World Judo Championships and at the 2019 World Judo Championships. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Moroccan male judoka Category:African Games medalists in judo Category:African Games silver medalists for Morocco Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games Category:African Games competitors for Morocco
